OL,5, A boy who suffered "catastrophic brain 
OL,6, injuries" when doctors failed to see he
OL,7, had a virus and sent him home after he 
OL,8, had a seizure has been awarded _27m.   
OL,10,FThe boy, who cannot be identified but  
OL,11,Fis now 13, suffered seizures as a      
OL,12,Ftoddler more than a decade ago.        
OL,14,FDetails of the settlement between the  
OL,15,Fboy's father and Liverpool's Alder Hey 
OL,16,FChildren's NHS Foundation Trust were   
OL,17,Fpublished in a written ruling.         
OL,19,FHigh Court judge Mr Justice Fordham    
OL,20,Fsaid it was a "sensible settlement".   
